{
  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 26",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Jon III</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Cave_near_Greyguard\" title=\"Cave near Greyguard\">cave near Greyguard</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n294 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_15\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 15\">Jon II</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_25\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 25\">Davos III</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jon III</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_27\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 27\">Daenerys III</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 30\">Jon IV</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Prior to climbing the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> sleep together in a <a href=\"/index.php/Grotto\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grotto\">grotto</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Mentions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Mentions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg/300px-Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"312\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dd/Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg/450px-Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dd/Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg/600px-Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Simonetti_Jon_Ygritte.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Grotto\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grotto\">grotto</a>, by Marc Simonetti ©</div></div></div>\n<p>The wildling band led by <a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a> stay in a <a href=\"/index.php/Cave_near_Greyguard\" title=\"Cave near Greyguard\">cave near Greyguard</a> the night before the planned attempt to scale the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a> that he cannot come with him, and that they will meet again at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>.\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a> force Jon to tell themmore about the patrols the <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> use along the Wall. <a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a> and Styr plan to climb the Wall between <a href=\"/index.php/Stonedoor\" title=\"Stonedoor\">Stonedoor</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Greyguard\" title=\"Greyguard\">Greyguard</a>, where a hill rests against the Wall, making for a shorter climb.\n</p><p>Later, Jon and <a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a> spend time in a cavern which supposedly leads from the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a> all the way beneath the Wall and beyond, but no one since <a href=\"/index.php/Gendel\" title=\"Gendel\">Gendel</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Gorne\" title=\"Gorne\">Gorne</a>, the legendary <a href=\"/index.php/Wildling\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildling\">wildling</a> brother kings, knows the way. As they make love, Ygritte asks Jon to stay with her and hide in this cavern forever.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>Appearing:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ghost\" title=\"Ghost\">Ghost</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grigg_the_Goat\" title=\"Grigg the Goat\">Grigg the Goat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jarl\" title=\"Jarl\">Jarl</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Styr\" title=\"Styr\">Styr</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ygritte\" title=\"Ygritte\">Ygritte</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:50;\">\n<p><b>Mentioned:</b>\n</p>\n<div style=\"column-count:2; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Alfyn_Crowkiller\" title=\"Alfyn Crowkiller\">Alfyn Crowkiller</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arson_Iceaxe\" title=\"Arson Iceaxe\">Arson Iceaxe</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bael_the_Bard\" title=\"Bael the Bard\">Bael the Bard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Craster\" title=\"Craster\">Craster</a>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Craster%27s_wives\" title=\"Craster&#39;s wives\">Craster's daughters</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dalla\" title=\"Dalla\">Dalla</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gendel\" title=\"Gendel\">Gendel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gorne\" title=\"Gorne\">Gorne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Theon_Greyjoy\" title=\"Theon Greyjoy\">Theon Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Harma\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Harma\">Harma</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Longspear_Ryk\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Longspear Ryk\">Longspear Ryk</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Luwin\" title=\"Luwin\">Luwin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Denys_Mallister\" title=\"Denys Mallister\">Denys Mallister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jeor_Mormont\" title=\"Jeor Mormont\">Jeor Mormont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Old_Nan\" title=\"Old Nan\">Old Nan</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Orell\" title=\"Orell\">Orell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qhorin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Qhorin\">Qhorin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_Qorgyle\" title=\"Lord Commander Qorgyle\">Lord Commander Qorgyle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rattleshirt\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Rattleshirt\">Rattleshirt</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mance_Rayder\" title=\"Mance Rayder\">Mance Rayder</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddison_Tollett\" title=\"Eddison Tollett\">Eddison Tollett</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Val\" title=\"Val\">Val</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Weeper\" title=\"Weeper\">Weeper</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions\">Mentions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_26&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Mentions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Houses:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Stark\" title=\"House Stark\">House Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Umber\" title=\"House Umber\">House Umber</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\" title=\"Eastwatch-by-the-Sea\">Eastwatch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Fist_of_the_First_Men\" title=\"Fist of the First Men\">Fist of the First Men</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Frostfangs\" title=\"Frostfangs\">Frostfangs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gorne%27s_Way\" title=\"Gorne&#39;s Way\">Gorne's Way</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Greyguard\" title=\"Greyguard\">Greyguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Grotto\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Grotto\">Grotto</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Milkwater\" title=\"Milkwater\">Milkwater</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Nightfort\" title=\"Nightfort\">Nightfort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sev